snippet.title: TECHNOVIKING! (Captioned)
snippet.description:
JUST REMEMBER! THE TECHNOVIKING DOESN'T DANCE TO THE MUSIC! THE MUSIC DANCES TO THE TECHNOVIKING!

Speaking of the music, we've located the first song in the video. The volume is low but you can edit it if you want. Unsure on the actual name.
http://www.rapidshare.com/files/67262725/techno_viking_song.mp3

Technoviking Is A Living God.

Some random person decided to steal my video and posted it on break.com and it now has over 2,500,000 views there as well.
http://www.break.com/index/techno-viking-with-captions.html

Internet superstar!
http://revision3.com/lilsuperstar/2008-02-21technoviking/
